{"tid":398393,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung Pay 推動八達通霸權","createTime":"2017-09-13T07:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T10:07:25.000Z","uid":731,"like":21,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6369488785698fcfbd2038c0d6a6baf4e2fe98fa","tid":398393,"uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:14:02.000Z","msg":"平時出街搭車，發現唔記得帶銀包，無八達通，咁點算？似乎未來有三星手機，就可以搞掂！在今日三星發佈會上，Galaxy Note8 固然是重要，但三星在會上公佈了一個更重要的消息，就係 Samsung Pay 將會加入一個好震撼的功能，而且同全香港每一個人都好有關！想知？睇下文啦！<br />\n<br />\n三星在發佈會上提到，Samsung Pay 將會能夠結合八達通卡，雖然三星暫時尚未提及到詳情，但版主估計，Samsung Pay 有機會能夠取替八達通卡，出街搭車就算無八達通卡，有 Samsung Pay 一樣可以嘟到機！如果係真的話，網友覺得正唔正先？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1141/25433/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fnb%2Ftalk%2F1141%2F25433%2F1%2F&d=Fiapx9xV0uLnJffjTeDtImi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=734aaf76\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1141/25433/1/</a>"},{"pid":"6a2c855532a13e82057803e1c8d9b598bb3e5bec","tid":398393,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:08:43.000Z","msg":"有人用咩"},{"pid":"1ed3c9ed8f14541021e1d5524518a0f29886f02d","tid":398393,"uid":59835,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人用咩</blockquote><br />\n竟然有人唔用八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6937b802cf0876e1a021f76f0db5a37f5178e3dc","tid":398393,"uid":4519,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:36:51.000Z","msg":"有得3叔pay，即係會有其他pay啦，時間問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6aa33e724383d75a35e967f93ae1b73a7b0d50","tid":398393,"uid":37820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:42:00.000Z","msg":"八達通會咁好死？"},{"pid":"9d47efa7d00a3d88a5b54e1c39c23dcb223d5a14","tid":398393,"uid":53902,"like":1,"dislike"